{"tid":404533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】強國小姐弟2分鐘內接連墮樓 街坊齊伸手都接唔住","createTime":"2017-09-18T07:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T09:07:07.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1a8e3b547939a1e8ea21936408fb0eecc8f3e4","tid":404533,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170917/large/1505663557_c785.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170917%2Flarge%2F1505663557_c785.jpg&h=794342d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n父母外出上班，獨留年幼子女在家，隨時釀悲劇！廣東東莞一對小姐弟，被外出的父親反鎖在位於3樓的房間內，未料卻相繼於2分鐘內接連墮下，姐姐落地後，大批街坊聞聲趕到現場，隨即看到弟弟墮下，眾人紛紛伸手希望接住他，卻沒能成功。姐弟都身受重傷，目前仍在醫院留醫。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上周五（15日）下午，該對小姐弟的母親外出工作，父親將他們從幼稚園接回家後，就反鎖在3樓家中，自己再前住上班。小姐弟在房間內玩，其間姐姐拿了一張小凳爬到露台上，不慎從3樓墮下，她墮下時險將一名路經的紅色女子砸到。<br />\n<br />\n女童墮樓後，紅衣女子大聲呼救，多民街坊走上前，往上一看，就見弟弟正爬到露台找姐姐，趕緊叫他返回房內，但這時男童已經跌下，街坊紛紛伸手試圖將他接住，但都不成功。<br />\n<br />\n事後姐弟被送院搶救，男童腹部受傷，姐姐則是胸部多處損傷。當地鎮政府指，目前男童已脫離危險，女童則已轉院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170918/57222129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170918%2F57222129&d=qjisSiChuLuju8hXnyZbiAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=fc9a95eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170918%2F57222129&h=a5528b3a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170918/57222129</a><br />\n條LINK有片<br />\n差一步就撞正個紅衫女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a601b588c0b4ae5572100a4e746542de6bf50da6","tid":404533,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"佢地真係想好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05b20f183f136f3896b9856906d261e556c3ed1","tid":404533,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地真係想好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n刷首抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18eb5b22b7cf454d1e2e6c31c8d30fc7f588299","tid":404533,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"個紅衫女人真係好彩，差少少⋯"},{"pid":"6a66706bc0e5b0bd996a174c2c344f685e3f7dea","tid":404533,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個紅衫女人真係好彩，差少少⋯</blockquote><br />\n如果撞中左實好猛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca5eb27125462d1899a23d1047eb08cb6d7266c","tid":404533,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:07:07.000Z","msg":"姐係咁囉 我覺得冇支那人死到係冇咩新聞價值囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}